sdr.deathRecord

Element Certifier

Documentation:
The certifier of the death record. Corresponds to items 45, 46, 47, 48 and 49 of the [U.S. Standard Certificate of Death](https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/dvs/DEATH11-03final-ACC.pdf).
